          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Summer Meals and Learning Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Education to award grants to state library administrative agencies to enable them to award subgrants to eligible local educational agencies for summer early reading programs held at schools with a summer lunch site. </p>]]></text>
